Interface HwISA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HwResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HwISAImpl

    public interface HwISA
extends HwResource
    A representation of the model object 'Hw ISA'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Family
    • Inst Width
    • Type
    See Also:
    HwComputingPackage.getHwISA()
